  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8305113">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8305113/" class="title-link">勘误？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8305113"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/maerta/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1070839-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/maerta/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">冇有</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-01-22"
      class="main-meta">2017-01-22 00:49:17</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8305113_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  p004，第三段是《联邦条款》，第四段是《邦联条款》。——下文和附录都说是签订了《邦联条款》。 p047，第三段“合众国的众议院由各州州议会选举两名参议员组成之”。——此处应该是参议院？ p057，第四段，“期中选举”？印象中媒体新闻报道还是美剧电影一般采用“中期选举”...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8305113/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8305113_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8305113_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










